===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|swāpan}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*swaipaną}}. Cognate with Early Mod. West Frisian {{m|fy|swiepe||whip, cleanse, sweep}}, from Old Frisian {{m|ofs|swēpa}}, {{m|ofs|suepa||sweep}}. See also {{m|en|swoop}}.

