{{en-verb|sweeps|sweeping|swept}}

# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[clean]] (a surface) by means of a [[stroke#Verb|stroking]] motion of a [[broom]] or [[brush]].
#: ''to '''sweep''' a floor, the street, or a chimney''
